{"tid":1631451,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"記住，依家中國共產黨係動用傾國之力搞連登/搞散運動","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T18:24:33.000Z","uid":201464,"like":237,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"80ef39c1a30dc4bacef47a603506368d27528b28","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"928就ddos<br />\n見101 ddos失敗（連仔cloudflare暗中做咗好多嘢大家未必知）<br />\n再加上開槍事件嚴重落維尼帝面<br />\n中共大為震怒<br />\n於是叫港共故意立「蒙面法」挑動大家情緒<br />\n並動用極大量五毛「轉為支持運動」<br />\n再不斷開分化post/煽動無差別破壞/攻擊post<br />\n務求搞散運動<br />\n再屈某啲post係分化post/左膠post<br />\n再配合狗/國安臥底扮示威者<br />\n進行無差別破壞/攻擊<br />\n（懷疑中原地產/港台記者/九龍塘爆車/火燒觀塘站/火車就係呢班人做，不過手足做嘅都唔割）<br />\n所以呢幾日係成個運動以嚟未試過有咁多五毛分化煽動<br />\n所以大家一定要頂住"},{"pid":"d00a5f05ddd8b1eed2064da12338c990534d340d","tid":1631451,"uid":75959,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e8b138cb7630896697403384d69dbeee22581c67","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"4589c0507e39009faa8602e7b7d964ea15c1a562","tid":1631451,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"唔割，但可改善"},{"pid":"de47252e7a8b86e7fd60f3678d82d2aad94fecfe","tid":1631451,"uid":114090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:36:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"489fb924ba229acdc0e1d403c2636850fb18732b","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4589c0507e39009faa8602e7b7d964ea15c1a562","tid":1631451,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"唔割，但可改善"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:37:11.000Z","msg":"記住依家係開盡晒國家機器"},{"pid":"6311940bc93e1c9b3a900d9544f28d67f9900996","tid":1631451,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:38:38.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"9eac08b2b61ab89df405178ea224127e1119161b","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:39:05.000Z","msg":"記住依家係開盡晒國家機器"},{"pid":"9d67fe7f1e52f2d04b2797d8478ee084417c27f7","tid":1631451,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"頂住啊大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796a7cda17c5d64f43e8ea82dd14c8690c5aa933","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"記住依家係開盡晒<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國家機器</span></em></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3071eb82cde4f3919f9ffce8f13a8cb2af2a81b3","tid":1631451,"uid":185974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2b69f98ac7c82639ef76423a62aee6c98e7728c","tid":1631451,"uid":64159,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:23.000Z","msg":"唔ddos = 大量五毛帶風向<br />\nddos = 等你睇唔到最新資訊"},{"pid":"a14fe61a90f6e8488870229f80213061570b4dda","tid":1631451,"uid":54678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"出面twitter reddit 好多五毛打緊文宣戰<br />\n識英文既巴打幫下拖"},{"pid":"168c6867150d13d3b3112103e79628893fce44c6","tid":1631451,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e5a76027c11273584d07fb7b290d282e5ae00f9","tid":1631451,"uid":82639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"中共咁急 我地就要慢慢黎<br />\n睇定啲<br />\n<br />\n出左緊急法，根本我地咩都唔做，都大把外媒屌。<br />\n<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆借力打力。"},{"pid":"47063a999205bcc1cb99476a89fdfa1c779cc858","tid":1631451,"uid":10722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n連登比到盡幾十萬會員<br />\n共匪閒閒地派幾百萬人黎吹風 冇可能頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有事事靠自己做多步 fact check"},{"pid":"9e1c8f3b8791cdb5d19c20256ee4727695609fac","tid":1631451,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:27.000Z","msg":"所以大家呢排睇連登要保持警惕，唔好跟車太貼，唔好比人講幾句就煽到，要無時無刻批判思考每一個post 係有道理定有疑點"},{"pid":"74cc5f9711a97ff26cbca79a88fea0b8edd6933b","tid":1631451,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6004305b5cb28d66e0de72a6582fab9cd262838d","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔ddos = 大量五毛帶風向<br />\nddos = 等你睇唔到最新資訊</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係101 ddos俾連仔cloudflare擋晒先行大量五毛帶風向呢個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7bc002831a033e9488e6a5cd6a3e7ad805eb66","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"bd72fa377349eb9a02e45822863deab647458df1","tid":1631451,"uid":72888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"52bf9bc286c7a660499abc34b97c90ffd57fc068","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"baaad45536103b79e1d5dd993817f9ec6a0be3a8","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"bc501f4476997fdab6491749a661fd8a3e1d83cb","tid":1631451,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:20.000Z","