化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1170802b956ab3a7c6bea5215e1665bc29395e1c","tid":1631451,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果星期一晚18區開花失敗  就代表大家默許左呢條惡法</span><br />\n因為第日市面會如常運作<br />\n大家星期五講到有幾嬲有幾難接受 原來到上班日馬照跑舞照跳既?<br />\ncarrie仲有咩好驚呀?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10月7號 18區啊 夜晚8點呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33EUVX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33EUVX5.jpg&h=293eada8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">18區呀<br />\n18區呀</span></span><br />\n罷工文宣啊<br />\n行動Post呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求下大家打返一場靚既三罷 起碼要8.5既級數先</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈建議和武合一令星期二香城真正變死城<