rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:16:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得係101 ddos俾連仔cloudflare擋晒先行大量五毛帶風向呢個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd64c74447fbed5ebcc2f60bacd2ed9390a39c4","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"eb8262b5fc46aff04aaa8389c1c2b8c513da2890","tid":1631451,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80ef39c1a30dc4bacef47a603506368d27528b28","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"928就ddos<br />\n見101 ddos失敗（連仔cloudflare暗中做咗好多嘢大家未必知）<br />\n再加上開槍事件嚴重落維尼帝面<br />\n中共大為震怒<br />\n於是叫港共故意立「蒙面法」挑動大家情緒<br />\n並動用極大量五毛「轉為支持運動」<br />\n再不斷開分化post/煽動無差別破壞/攻擊post<br />\n務求搞散運動<br />\n再屈某啲post係分化post/左膠post<br />\n再配合狗/國安臥底扮示威者<br />\n進行無差別破壞/攻擊<br />\n（懷疑中原地產/港台記者/九龍塘爆車/火燒觀塘站/火車就係呢班人做，不過手足做嘅都唔割）<br />\n所以呢幾日係成個運動以嚟未試過有咁多五毛分化煽動<br />\n所以大家一定要頂住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:41:29.000Z","msg":"不割唔代表唔檢討<br />\n另外大家完全忘記左be water"},{"pid":"4e5ebbc2448f56db90ccdb03199c8791c07a14b1","tid":1631451,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:06:27.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"5f89d23eada3f097ae5bda1593e10cf60b88b6a1","tid":1631451,"uid":293814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:11:21.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"202f9d050e64aa1f39a63233090234d331b8f100","tid":1631451,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:37:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8e1baae20fa525a56eaed96b3c7ec4da257c53a","tid":1631451,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:38:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">待到秋來九月八<br />\n我花開後百花殺</span></span>"},{"pid":"8c6e58d1bd14489320c6cd924fc92ab424fbaab3","tid":1631451,